{"tid":1195103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜稱「我不知道，我不曉得」香港反送中遊行","createTime":"2019-06-09T14:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T00:51:51.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"088bfd3ecc4aee45d3d5e9810adf05492e8c4a82","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜稱不知港反送中遊行 綠委錯愕<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜9日率高雄市政府首長，參與高雄龍舟大賽，<span style=\"color: red;\">面對媒體詢問香港「反送中條款遊行」看法，韓國瑜竟連回稱「我不知道，我不曉得」</span>，讓民進黨立委何志偉相當錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜9日結束龍舟競賽活動後，接受媒體訪問，媒體第一題即提問對香港「反送中條款遊行」看法，韓國瑜竟僅回應「我不知道，我不曉得」，主辦單位隨即出聲請媒體詢問活動主題。<br />\n<br />\n對此民進黨立委何志偉遺憾表示，「或許回答不知道不曉得，是最簡單的答案，但也是最不好的答案」，何志偉指出「或許對韓市長而言，不去挑釁中國是對的，但是選擇看不見或表達不知道，又是對的嗎」，何志偉表示「未來可能的總統候選人，要怎麼面對中國的爭議問題，難道都只看經濟層面喊發大財，其他就可以視而不見？」何志偉反問「韓市長呼籲支持者揮國旗穿國旗裝，請問中華民國的價值又是什麼，韓粉看到韓市長如此回應，又可以接受嗎」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%B6%A0%E5%A7%94%E9%8C%AF%E6%84%95-125523843.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E5%25A7%2594%25E9%258C%25AF%25E6%2584%2595-125523843.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4yL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=ee141b10\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E7%B6%A0%E5%A7%94%E9%8C%AF%E6%84%95-125523843.html</a>"},{"pid":"96ca9a8b95e98328679ea64833e34fdcd550604f","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:03:47.000Z","msg":"只知道發大財"},{"pid":"ecfa5d0c86eb36e341ad58ff264b9c6731dc2be7","tid":1195103,"uid":163291,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"錢錢錢<br />\n只要舔中共鞋底就有錢<br />\n台灣人選韓國瑜就真係做狗<br />\n中國台灣省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ad7bdd30e6241faec9d95fe15bd144b3aa70c5","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZpVb5y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZpVb5y.jpg&h=fc01c1ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f26bf1e6e04d39fdb2ec2d41a900c8fc2539e603","tid":1195103,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"送中發大財"},{"pid":"b2744ff99b37f254e6982e8262353a034dd5a9dd","tid":1195103,"uid":186087,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"咁都選到。<br />\n 台灣選民係醒ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb03dc783602d99eedb2d39259c35d2c7af249cc","tid":1195103,"uid":19678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"36bc1c062e21076404979ddeeb6121a0b7a51468","tid":1195103,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"原來除左發大財之外仲識講其他野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4634021fdca58102ecdc921a647bcdcfd2acd2","tid":1195103,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"高雄挺送中<br />\n香港發大財<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935315e42808960bea7a25f266e0c3e46d2de331","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/teNfj_328hE..hEiIrsiqQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/e84d9d61e0d4bcdf783686127f2a8208\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FteNfj_328hE..hEiIrsiqQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fe84d9d61e0d4bcdf783686127f2a8208&h=e339be5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e67c17e5ef146124e35ebe454c106225943deb54","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:05:19.000Z","msg":"香港反送中遊行 郭台銘：一國兩制失敗<br />\n<br />\n最新更新：2019/06/09 <br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者王承中台北9日電）鴻海董事長郭台銘今天針對香港爆發反送中遊行表示，他認為香港的一國兩制是失敗的，這也是當初他力勸高雄市長韓國瑜不要進中聯辦的原因。他說：「我們必須堅持中華民國自由民主的制度。」<br />\n<br />\n香港泛民主派今天為反對政府修訂逃犯條例而發起「反送中」遊行。在遊行前，泛民方面全力呼籲支持者上街遊行，民間人權陣線估計，這場遊行的人數和規模，可能超越2003年震驚海外的「7.1」大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n港府4月左右向立法會提出修訂草案，希望今後可以個案形式與台灣和中國大陸移交逃犯，但泛民方面一直反對。泛民將這次遊行定性為「反送中」，即反對政府修訂逃犯條例草案，原因是不相信中國大陸的司法制度可以保障被移交者的人權，以及擔心成為遣送政治犯的缺口。<br />\n<br />\n爭取國民黨總統提名的郭台銘則指出，他認為香港的一國兩制是失敗的，這也是為什麼他當初力勸高雄市長韓國瑜不要進中聯辦的原因，「我們必須堅持中華民國自由民主的制度」。國民黨今天表示，對於香港遊行保持密切關注，同時期盼各方能夠理性溝通，事件和平落幕。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201906090187.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faipl%2F201906090187.aspx&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4yL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=d1af6c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201906090187.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"b98d911d852820a4a57f9c72c7b840e3d9a951f8","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"賴清德聲援香港反送中 譴責中國戕害人權<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-09<br />\n<br />\n香港民間人權陣線今天發起反修訂「逃犯條例」的大遊行，行政院前院長賴清德稍早在臉書聲援，他表示，今天在銅鑼灣維園草坪展開一場抗議活動，反對香港政府強推「逃犯條例」修訂，這是被公認的「惡法」，一旦草案通過，過境香港的台灣人，只要被中國認定為犯罪並發布通緝，就可能被捕並移交中國受審。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">賴清德說，他要強力譴責戕害人權，藐視民主自由的粗暴手段，也對勇敢站出來的香港民眾，表達聲援與祝福。他說，台灣已經是主權獨立的國家，中國的這種違反普世價值的行為，更加證明「一國兩制」的欺瞞與空洞，台灣絕對不會接受這樣框架，更拒絕成為第二個西藏、第二個香港。</span><br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"3bf6a3247a51524301857fad7dabbaafb1ab37e3","tid":1195103,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"香港發大財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f159199d49b6228a96dea0d0335b264c946e1fab","tid":1195103,"uid":234704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"2004年因違反交通規則在閃紅燈路口未先停車而撞死人，被法院判處6個月有期徒刑，緩刑2年。<br />\n<br />\n撞死人發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c329a80a12eca97f79b508eaa2c9227dec4542","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"四個總統兩黨內參選人<br />\n3個支持香港取消逃犯條例修訂<br />\n只有入過中聯辦支那瑜回應<br />\n什麼都不知道"},{"pid":"b2a9276c6704db5bd10a495352337d7bfd9320e2","tid":1195103,"uid":41821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢條76仆街死啦屌"},{"pid":"619a6141d0862cf48a82e9b18ce02479f97ae3b3","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"唔明佢民調點解咁高？"},{"pid":"68bc7f00c999fd26050049d776b75e1fa8205f8b","tid":1195103,"uid":166190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"935315e42808960bea7a25f266e0c3e46d2de331","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/teNfj_328hE..hEiIrsiqQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/e84d9d61e0d4bcdf783686127f2a8208\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FteNfj_328hE..hEiIrsiqQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NTEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fe84d9d61e0d4bcdf783686127f2a8208&h=e339be5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966487851701697cb33a32f51ec175c364f716b0","tid":1195103,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"地下黨支部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e33c3ec56f566b384ac331107ac652d827aeff","tid":1195103,"uid":121255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"郭台銘真係醒過佢多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd991f4f5140086b27839fb62d8eb9099d801f13","tid":1195103,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91e33c3ec56f566b384ac331107ac652d827aeff","tid":1195103,"uid":121255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"郭台銘真係醒過佢多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"郭台銘....佢係咁多個候選人入面最醒，無論侵侵連任與否佢嘅勝算都係最大。<br />\n<br />\n但我個人麻麻佢。"},{"pid":"61702108afd5c615d86981d3c42403cd81cd44b7","tid":1195103,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91e33c3ec56f566b384ac331107ac652d827aeff","tid":1195103,"uid":121255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"郭台銘真係醒過佢多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-